<p>France’s Louvre Museum says it will fully restore Empress Eugénie’s emerald crown after it was damaged in an October museum heist. The museum has now released photos showing how badly the crown was crushed. Investigators are still working to track down other objects taken in the raid.</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/vXxV83IEao4FqurTNNhH0XIGIJzQJAqTZzIJ2BP-iRJxIc6xjXXCjPh-QN_aUGqrTRIQeUnU-3hg9ty22PW1Ngol-L8kX-5fe5HwHT9oH_C3tTbTnt6l-oYw5jR_2ch9l9HNND3VqfiSnw8GQeBbJf1IdH4vhu7jK3l4MqGP-3qaPtNPJw' alt='The damaged crown of Empress Eugenie after it was dropped during the heist from the Louvre Museum on October 19, 2025.' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>First public look: The Louvre says these newly published photos are the first images released since the October theft.</li><li>Recovered outside: The thieves dropped the crown during their escape, and it was found on the sidewalk outside the museum.</li><li>Loot still missing: DW says eight other items taken in the heist still haven’t been recovered.</li></ul><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Louvre Museum: The museum said the crown was &quot;crushed and significantly misshapen&quot; and promised a full restoration. (<a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/france/article/2026/02/05/theft-at-the-louvre-empress-eugenie-s-crown-damaged-in-robbery-museum-vows-full-restoration_6750192_7.html'>Le Monde</a>)</li><li>BBC: The BBC highlighted the museum’s assessment that the crown was badly deformed but still &quot;intact,&quot; framing the images as the first look since the theft. (<a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cn40ev200yjo'>BBC</a>)</li><li>Deutsche Welle: DW emphasized that the crown was dropped during the getaway and noted that eight stolen pieces have not yet been found. (<a href='https://www.dw.com/en/louvre-to-fully-restore-empress-eugenie-s-crown-after-heist/a-75824933'>Deutsche Welle</a>)</li><li>The New York Times: The New York Times focused on the aftermath of the heist and the extent of the visible damage now shown in official images. (<a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/05/world/europe/louvre-heist-crown-damage-eugenie-empress.html'>The New York Times</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://www.nytimes.com/2026/02/05/world/europe/louvre-heist-crown-damage-eugenie-empress.html'>The Louvre Thieves Dropped This Priceless Crown. Now It Looks Like This.</a> - nytimes.com</li><li><a href='https://www.dw.com/en/louvre-to-fully-restore-empress-eugenie-s-crown-after-heist/a-75824933'>Louvre to fully restore Empress Eugenie&#x27;s crown after heist</a> - dw.com</li><li><a href='https://www.lemonde.fr/en/france/article/2026/02/05/theft-at-the-louvre-empress-eugenie-s-crown-damaged-in-robbery-museum-vows-full-restoration_6750192_7.html'>Louvre heist: Empress Eugénie&#x27;s crown damaged in robbery, museum vows full restoration</a> - lemonde.fr</li><li><a href='https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cn40ev200yjo'>Louvre Museum crown left crushed but &#x27;intact&#x27; after raid</a> - bbc.com</li></ul>